{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban and criminalise all abortions. Choose Adoption and Save Children\u2019s Lives",
        "additional_details": "We believe our Society should Protect the Sacred Gift of Life especially Innocent Children In The Womb the Sick & Helpless We believe Life Is From Conception No Exceptions Until A Natural Death. We believe every Life is Worth Living & a Civilised Society offers Families Palliative Care Hope, Love, Kindness not death. We believe the Bill is a radical change to the law of our land which until now recognised that an unborn child has the Right to Life. Choose instead Adoption & Save Children\u2019s Lives",
        "background": "The Crime and Policing Bill includes a clause which would mean that in respect of any law involving abortion, a woman would not commit an offence if acting in relation to her own pregnancy. We did not ask for this. It was not in any manifesto. We demand that abortion be abolished and criminalised.",
